Bootstrap: docker
FROM: osgeo/gdal:ubuntu-full-latest

%labels
    Author gtamkin
    Version v2.0.0

%help
===========================================================================
	- cisto-gdal-ubuntu â€“ contains the Python data science ecosystem:
